\c 1
\s Kuzvarwa kwaSamueri
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwaiva neumwe murume weRamataimi-Zofimi wegomo raEfuremu\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*, uye zita rake raiva Erikana, mwanakomana waJerohamu, mwanakomana waErihu, mwanakomana waTohu, mwanakomana waZufi\x + 1 Makor. 6.22,26,27,34,35.\x* muEfurati\x + Gen.. 35.19.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino waiva nevakadzi vaviri; zita reumwe raiva Hana, uye zita reumwe raiva Penina. Zvino Penina waiva nevana, asi Hana waiva asina vana\x + Vato. 13.2. Ruk. 1.7.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino murume uyu waikwira kubva muguta rake gore negore\x + Eki. 23.14. Ruk. 2.41.\x* kunonamata nekubaira kuna Jehovha wehondo\x + Det. 12.5,6,7.\x* paShiro\x + Josh. 18.1.\x*. Uye vanakomana vaviri vaEri, Hofini naPinehasi vapristi vaJehovha vaivapo.
\p
\v 4 Zvino rakati rava zuva Erikana ndokubaira, ndokupa kuna Penina mukadzi wake nevanakomana vake nevanasikana vake vose migove;
\v 5 asi Hana wakamupa mugove wakapetwa kaviri; nokuti waida Hana, asi Jehovha waiva avhara chizvaro chake\x + Det. 12.17,18. 16.11.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino muvengi wake wakamushungurudzawo nekumurwadzisa, kuti amutsamwise, nokuti Jehovha waiva avhara chizvaro chake\x + Job. 24.21.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino wakaita saizvozvo gore negore kubva paanokwira kuimba yaJehovha; saka wakamutsamwisa; naizvozvo wakachema ndokusadya.
\v 8 Zvino Erikana murume wake wakati kwaari: Hana, unochemei? Uye sei usingadyi? Zvino sei moyo wako une shungu? Handina kukunakira kupfuura vanakomana gumi here\x + Rut. 4.15.\x*?
\p
\v 9 Naizvozvo Hana wakasimuka shure kwekudya paShiro\x + Josh. 18.1.\x*, uye shure kwekunwa. Zvino Eri mupristi waiva agere pachigaro pagwatidziro remukova wetembere yaJehovha\x + 3.3.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino \add Hana\add* waiva mukurwadziwa pamoyo, ndokunyengetera kuna Jehovha, ndokuchema misodzi kwazvo\x + Job. 7.11. 10.1.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino wakapika mhiko\x + Vato. 11.30.\x*, ndokuti: Jehovha wehondo, kana mukatarira zvekutarira kutambudzika kwemurandakadzi wenyu\x + Gen.. 29.32. 2 Sam. 16.12.\x*, uye mukandirangarira, nekusakanganwa murandakadzi wenyu, asi mukapa murandakadzi wenyu mwana munhurume, zvino ndichamupa kuna Jehovha mazuva ose eupenyu hwake\x + 1.19. Gen.. 8.1.\x*. Zvino chisvo hachingauyi pamusoro wake\x + Vato. 13.5.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino zvakaitika paaienderera mberi kunyengetera pamberi paJehovha, kuti Eri wakacherekedza muromo wake.
\v 13 Zvino Hana waitaura mumoyo make; miromo yake yoga yaifamba, asi inzwi rake raiva risinganzwikwi; naizvozvo Eri wakafunga kuti wakadhakwa.
\v 14 Eri ndokuti kwaari: Kusvika rinhi wakadhakwa? Bvisa waini yako kwauri.
\v 15 Hana ndokupindura ndokuti: Kwete, ishe wangu, ndiri mukadzi wemweya unoshungurudzika; handina kunwa waini kana zvinwiwa zvinodhaka, asi ndadurura mweya wangu pamberi paJehovha\x + Job. 30.16. Map. 42.4. Map. 62.8. Marir. 2.19.\x*.
\v 16 Musabata murandakadzi wenyu semwanasikana waBheriari\x + Det. 13.13. 15.9.\x*, nokuti ndataura pakuwanda kwekuchema kwangu nekutambudzika kwangu kusvika ikozvino.
\v 17 Eri ndokupindura ndokuti: Enda nerugare\x + 25.35. 20.13,42. 2 Sam. 15.9. 2 Madz. 5.19. Mako 5.34. Ruk. 7.50. 8.48.\x*; uye Mwari waIsraeri ngaape chikumbiro chako chawakumbira kwaari\x + Map. 20.4,5.\x*.
\v 18 Iye ndokuti: Murandakadzi wenyu ngaawane tsitsi pameso enyu\x + Gen.. 33.15.\x*. Naizvozvo mukadzi wakaenda nenzira yake, ndokudya; zvino chiso chake hachina kuzo\add suruvara\add*zve\x + Mup. 9.7.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Zvino vakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani, ndokunamata pamberi paJehovha, ndokudzokera ndokusvika kumba kwavo paRama\x + 1.1. 2.11. 7.17. 8.4. 15.34. 16.13. 19.18,19,22,23. 20.1. 25.1. 28.3. 9.16. Mat. 27.57.\x*. Erikana ndokuziva mukadzi wake Hana, Jehovha ndokumurangarira\x + 1.11.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino zvakaitika pakushanduka kwemazuva kuti Hana wakabata mimba, ndokubereka mwanakomana, ndokutumidza zita rake Samueri, nokuti \add wakati\add*: Ndakamukumbira kuna Jehovha\x + Eki. 18.4.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino murume Erikana neimba yake yose vakakwira kunobaira Jehovha chibairo chegore negore, nemhiko yake\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 22 Asi Hana haana kukwira, nokuti wakati kumurume wake: \add Handingakwiri\add* kusvika mwana arumurwa, ipapo ndichamuunza kuti aonekwe pamberi paJehovha, agogarapo kusvika rinhi narinhi\x + 1.11,28. 2.11,18. 3.1. Eki. 21.6. 2 Sam. 7.29.\x*.
\v 23 Erikana murume wake ndokuti kwaari: Ita zvakanaka pameso ako; gara kusvika wamurumura\x + Num.. 30.7.\x*; koga Jehovha ngaasimbise shoko rake\x + 2 Sam. 7.25.\x*. Naizvozvo mukadzi wakagara, ndokuyamwisa mwanakomana wake kusvika amurumura.
\p
\v 24 Zvino wakakwira naye paainge amurumura, ane nzombe diki nhatu, neefa imwe yeupfu hwakatsetseka, nedende rewaini\x + Det. 12.5,6,11.\x*, ndokumuunza muimba yaJehovha paShiro\x + 1.3,9. Josh. 18.1.\x*. Zvino mwana waiva mudiki.
\v 25 Zvino vakabaya nzombe diki, ndokuunza mwana kuna Eri.
\v 26 Zvino wakati: Haiwa ishe wangu, \add ne\add*upenyu hwemweya wenyu, ishe wangu, ndini mukadzi waiva amire nemwi pano kunyengetera kuna Jehovha\x + 17.55. 20.3. Gen.. 42.15. 2 Madz. 2.2,4,6. 4.30.\x*.
\v 27 Ndakanyengeterera mukomana uyu, zvino Jehovha wakandipa chikumbiro changu chandakakumbira kwaari\x + 1.17.\x*.
\v 28 Naizvozvo neni ndamupa kuna Jehovha, mazuva ose aaripo; wakakumbirwa kuna Jehovha\x + 1.11,22.\x*; zvino akanamata Jehovha ipapo\x + Gen.. 24.26,52.\x*.